## Launch Codes:
1. Clone this repository: `git clone https://github.com/kaitlynsandor/BidenTweetAnalysis.git`
2. Move into the app directory:  `cd BidenTweetAnalysis`    
3. Install the module(s) listed in the requirements.txt file.  
4. run python3 -m spacy download en
4. In a terminal session, `pip install -r requirements.txt`
5. Run the program: `python3 app.py`
